<FIRST>r w PM-PoliceMemorial     04-25 0266</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Police Memorial,250</SECOND>
<HEAD>Plans Due for Memorial Honoring Slain Police Officers</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
