<FIRST>u a PM-SubmarineFire-Sailors     04-25 0411</FIRST>
<SECOND>PM-Submarine Fire-Sailors,0427</SECOND>
<HEAD>Sailors Solemn on Return From Crippled Submarine</HEAD>
<HEAD>With PM-Submarine Fire</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By RON WORD</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MAYPORT NAVAL STATION, Fla. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
