<HEAD>Use of Coast Guard in Gulf Patrols Criticized</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-US-Gulf</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By TIM AHERN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
