TION> <ORGANIZATION> World </ORGANIZATION>'s one-day admission is $ 18.95 for adults and $ 15.95 for senior citizens -LRB- 55 and older -RRB- and children 3-11. A 12-month pass is $ 49 for adults and $ 39 for children. Founders Club pass, available until May 28, is $ 125 and offers special discounts and is good for admission through Dec. 31, 1991. Sea World sales office number is 512-523-3400. -RRB-
